org.apache.derbyTesting.unitTests.harness

Interface UnitTest

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BasicUnitTest, T_AccessFactory, T_b2i, T_CacheService, T_Cipher, T_CipherBlowfish, T_CipherCFB, T_CipherDES, T_CipherECB, T_CipherOFB, T_DaemonService, T_Diagnosticable, T_FileSystemData, T_Generic, T_Heap, T_Like, T_LockFactory, T_MarkedLimitInputStream, T_MultiIterations, T_MultiThreadedIterations, T_RawStoreFactory, T_RecoverBadLog, T_RecoverFullLog, T_Recovery, T_SortController, T_StreamFile, T_UUIDFactory, T_XA

    public interface UnitTest
    The UnitTest interface is implemented by the class that tests a class. Such a class has the name XUnitTest and is the test for the class named X.

    Version:
    0.1
